data.description: This 1949 timepiece is a perfect opportunity to live on a quiet street in the desireable Concordia / Alberta Arts area. Situated on an oversized 9450 square foot lot there is space to redevelop, have a gigantic garden, or install a pool! Hardwood floors on main floor, 2 fireplaces and spacious basement with bonus room, 2nd bathroom and family room. This home needs work and may not qualify for financing without repairs. House to be sold "as is".
